consequence
of the approaching fte.
We shall have a mild winter, for I have never
known the Herr Hofmeister so courteous;
observed
Roger de Blonay, while showing his guests
into the castle. Thy Bernese authorities,
Melchior
,
are little apt to be lavish of their
